sequenceDiagram
  participant Web as web/app.js
  participant GW as WebSocketGateway
  participant IPC as CodexIpcFeed
  participant Owner as Desktop/VS Code owner

  Web->>GW: set_active_conversation
  GW-->>Web: latest conversation_surface_snapshot
  GW-->>Web: follower_mode_changed

  Web->>GW: set_active_follower_mode(true)
  GW-->>Web: follower_mode_changed(enabled=true)

  Web->>GW: follower_send_message
  GW->>GW: validate follower mode + conversation status
  GW->>IPC: thread-follower-start-turn
  IPC->>Owner: IPC request
  Owner-->>IPC: response
  IPC-->>GW: ack/error
  GW-->>Web: follower_message_sent
  Owner-->>IPC: new thread-stream-state-changed
  IPC-->>GW: updated surface
  GW-->>Web: conversation_surface_snapshot
